    "body:0002": {
      "field": "body",
      "source": "Roles define what users are allowed to do, from simply visiting the platform to managing complex multi-project structures. Assigning the right roles ensures responsibilities are distributed efficiently, data privacy is respected, and users only access what they need.",
      "source_hash": "2b1a471446f6",
      "target": "Roles define what users are allowed to do, from simply visiting the platform to managing complex multi-project structures. Assigning the right roles ensures responsibilities are distributed efficiently, data privacy is respected, and users only access what they need.",
